📄 DOSYA 2: .gitignore
GitHub'ta: "Add file" → "Create new file"

Dosya adı:

.gitignore
İçerik (kopyalayın):

# Dependencies
node_modules/
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
ENV/

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.production

# Build
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log

# Database
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Testing
.coverage
htmlcov/
.pytest_cache/
